# Bunti Visual Validation Tape
# Focus: Static High-Fidelity Demos

Output scripts/demo.gif
Output scripts/demo.png

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

# 1. Icon Showcase
Type "bun demo icons"
Enter
Sleep 5s

# 2. Static Dashboard
Type "bun demo dashboard"
Enter
Sleep 5s
